Restart on the <span class="usb">final</span><span class="clone">new</span> Tails
=================================================================================

<div class="step-image">[[!img inc/infography/restart-on-final-tails.png link="no"]]</div>

1. Shut down the computer.

1. Unplug the <span class="usb">first</span><span class="clone">other</span> USB stick and leave the <span class="usb">second</span><span class="clone">new</span> USB stick plugged in.

1. Switch on the computer.

1. In the **Boot Tails** menu, choose **Live** and press **Enter**.

1. After 30&ndash;60 seconds, *Tails Greeter* appears.

1. In *Tails Greeter*, select your preferred language in the drop-down
list on the bottom left of the screen. Click **Login**.

1. After 15&ndash;30 seconds, the Tails desktop appears.
